---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  pageKey="about"
  title="Austin Copps — Generative-AI builder who ships solo"
  description="Lead AI Analyst at Worlds. Solo-ships commercial generative-AI applications end to end — from legal classifiers to camp-safety platforms."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative pt-6 md:pt-10 pb-20 md:pb-28">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start">
      <!-- Left: signal column -->
      <aside class="md:col-span-3 flex flex-col gap-6 md:pt-3">
        <p class="reveal font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">
          <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent rounded-full mr-2 align-middle animate-pulse"></span>
          Available for new work
        </p>
        <p class="reveal font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-300 leading-relaxed" style="transition-delay: 80ms;">
          Generative-AI builder<br />Dallas, TX<br />Established 2022
        </p>
        <div class="reveal hairline max-w-[120px]" style="transition-delay: 160ms;"></div>
        <p class="reveal font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-400 leading-relaxed" style="transition-delay: 240ms;">
          File 01<br />Personal index
        </p>
      </aside>

      <!-- Center/right: headline -->
      <div class="md:col-span-9">
        <h1
          class="reveal font-display font-light text-fluid-display text-ink-50 leading-[0.92] tracking-tightest"
          style="transition-delay: 60ms;"
        >
          I build AI<br />
          <span class="italic font-normal">that actually</span><br />
          ships.<span class="text-accent">_</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="reveal mt-10 md:mt-14 max-w-[58ch] text-fluid-lg text-ink-100 leading-relaxed" style="transition-delay: 220ms;">
          <p>
            Lead AI Analyst on a forward-deployed engineering team at
            <a class="link text-ink-50" href="https://worlds.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Worlds</a>.
            Outside of that, I solo-ship commercial applications — a contracted
            <span class="text-accent">appellate-court classifier</span>, a unified
            <span class="text-accent">recommendation system</span> for a merged periodontics company, and a
            <span class="text-accent">camp-safety platform</span> launching on the App Store.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6 md:gap-8" style="transition-delay: 320ms;">
          <a class="link font-mono text-mono-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-ink-50" href="/work">
            See work history&nbsp;&nbsp;→
          </a>
          <a class="link font-mono text-mono-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-ink-50" href="/projects">
            See projects&nbsp;&nbsp;→
          </a>
          <a
            class="link font-mono text-mono-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-ink-50"
            href="mailto:austin@austincopps.com"
          >
            Reach out&nbsp;&nbsp;→
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- "PROOF" stat strip -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 border-y border-ink-700">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-y-10 md:gap-x-8">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-400">Commercial apps shipped</p>
        <p class="mt-2 font-display font-light text-fluid-2xl text-ink-50">03 <span class="text-ink-400">·</span> <span class="text-ink-300 font-mono text-mono-sm align-middle">solo</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay: 80ms;">
        <p class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-400">AI solutions owned</p>
        <p class="mt-2 font-display font-light text-fluid-2xl text-ink-50">Entire <span class="text-ink-300 font-mono text-mono-sm align-middle">production portfolio</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay: 160ms;">
        <p class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-400">Cases / year at scale</p>
        <p class="mt-2 font-display font-light text-fluid-2xl text-ink-50">~2,000 <span class="text-ink-300 font-mono text-mono-sm align-middle">classified</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay: 240ms;">
        <p class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-400">Cost reduction via agentic redesign</p>
        <p class="mt-2 font-display font-light text-fluid-2xl text-ink-50">~90% <span class="text-ink-300 font-mono text-mono-sm align-middle">per query</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW I WORK -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
    <div class="md:col-span-4">
      <p class="reveal font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">02 — How I work</p>
      <h2 class="reveal mt-4 font-display font-light text-fluid-2xl tracking-tightest text-ink-50">
        End to end.<br />By myself.
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-10 gap-y-10">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-300">Discovery</p>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-readable text-fluid-base text-ink-100 leading-relaxed">
          I sit with the people who'll use the thing. Translate the messy reality into a shape an AI system can actually run on. No throwing it over the wall.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay: 80ms;">
        <p class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-300">Architecture</p>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-readable text-fluid-base text-ink-100 leading-relaxed">
          Pick the right model, the right retrieval, the right tools — and the right humans in the loop. Boring infra. Explainable outputs. Audit trails by default.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay: 160ms;">
        <p class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-300">Build & ship</p>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-readable text-fluid-base text-ink-100 leading-relaxed">
          Frontend, backend, mobile, deploys, CI, observability — handled. I use agentic AI on my own work, so the cycle from idea to deployed feature collapses.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay: 240ms;">
        <p class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-300">Maintain & iterate</p>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-readable text-fluid-base text-ink-100 leading-relaxed">
          I keep watching. Drift, edge cases, new feedback. Switchboard — my own internal ops platform — observes my products and tells me what to fix next.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CURRENTLY -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 border-t border-ink-700">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <p class="reveal font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">03 — Currently</p>
        <h2 class="reveal mt-4 font-display font-light text-fluid-2xl tracking-tightest text-ink-50">
          What I'm <span class="italic">on</span> right now.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="md:col-span-8 flex flex-col gap-8">
        <li class="reveal grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 items-baseline border-t border-ink-700 pt-6">
          <span class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-3 font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-300">
            JUN 2025 → NOW
          </span>
          <p class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-9 text-fluid-base text-ink-100 leading-relaxed">
            Leading the AI Analyst function at <span class="text-ink-50">Worlds</span>, running the entire production and pilot AI portfolio from a forward-deployed seat.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="reveal grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 items-baseline border-t border-ink-700 pt-6" style="transition-delay: 80ms;">
          <span class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-3 font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-300">
            JAN 2026 → IMMINENT
          </span>
          <p class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-9 text-fluid-base text-ink-100 leading-relaxed">
            Shipping <span class="text-ink-50">Chirp</span>, my camp-safety platform, to the iOS and Android stores.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="reveal grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 items-baseline border-t border-ink-700 pt-6" style="transition-delay: 160ms;">
          <span class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-3 font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-300">
            ONGOING
          </span>
          <p class="col-span-12 sm:col-span-9 text-fluid-base text-ink-100 leading-relaxed">
            Building agentic systems for my own ops — <span class="text-ink-50">Switchboard</span> and <span class="text-ink-50">Mechanic</span> — and applying every lesson back into client work.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- REACH OUT -->
  <section class="py-24 md:py-32 border-t border-ink-700">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="md:col-span-7">
        <p class="reveal font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">04 — Reach out</p>
        <h2 class="reveal mt-4 font-display font-light text-fluid-3xl tracking-tightest text-ink-50 leading-[0.95]">
          Have something hard <span class="italic">to ship?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="reveal mt-6 max-w-readable text-fluid-lg text-ink-100 leading-relaxed">
          I'm looking for generative-AI roles where the job is to build things and solve real problems. Contract or full-time. Talk to me.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-5 md:pt-6">
        <a class="reveal link group flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 border-t border-ink-700 pt-5" href="mailto:austin@austincopps.com">
          <span class="font-display font-light text-fluid-lg text-ink-50">austin@austincopps.com</span>
          <span class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-400 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">email</span>
        </a>
        <a class="reveal link group flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 border-t border-ink-700 pt-5" href="tel:+14696629792" style="transition-delay: 80ms;">
          <span class="font-display font-light text-fluid-lg text-ink-50">(469) 662-9792</span>
          <span class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-400 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">phone</span>
        </a>
        <a class="reveal link group flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 border-t border-ink-700 pt-5" href="https://linkedin.com/in/austin-copps-06332621b" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="transition-delay: 160ms;">
          <span class="font-display font-light text-fluid-lg text-ink-50">/in/austin-copps</span>
          <span class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-400 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">linkedin</span>
        </a>
        <a class="reveal link group flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 border-t border-ink-700 pt-5" href="https://github.com/austincopps" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="transition-delay: 240ms;">
          <span class="font-display font-light text-fluid-lg text-ink-50">@austincopps</span>
          <span class="font-mono text-mono-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-400 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">github</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
